South Korea plan step keep 1987 current account surplus below five billion dlrs Economic Planning Board Minister Kim Mahn-je said. Kim told reporter government repay loan ahead schedule encourage firm increase import investment abroad prevent current account surplus rise quickly. Last South Korea's current account surplus 4.65 billion dlrs. It widen 622 mln dlrs January 484 mln December compare deficit 334 mln January 1986 Bank Korea figure show. REUTER 